    <h2>Introduction to the StockIT Project</h2>
    <p>
        StockIT is a comprehensive web application designed to streamline inventory management for small to medium-sized businesses.
        This project aims to simplify the tracking, updating, and management of stock levels, providing businesses with a clear,
        real-time view of their inventory. As the lead developer on this project, my role has been to oversee the development process
